description: Retrieves all channel groups that are configured in Elemental MediaPackage.

nested_items.name: ChannelGroupName
nested_items.description: The name that describes the channel group. The name is the primary identifier for the channel group, and must be unique for your account in the AWS Region.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) associated with the resource.

nested_items.name: CreatedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time the channel group was created.

nested_items.name: ModifiedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time the channel group was modified.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: Any descriptive information that you want to add to the channel group for future identification purposes.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token from the GET list request. Use the token to fetch the next page of results.
